{"tid":1541732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲五毛造謠要坐7年監","createTime":"2019-09-04T15:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T08:07:58.000Z","uid":254898,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ed7b7cf1cabe3806d658c46b73c8e6a33f21ee","tid":1541732,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"各位藍絲五毛你們知道嗎？造謠要坐7年監<br />\n當你涉及造謠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你亦都係要負上有關既刑責<br />\n所以我勸喻你地依家停止造謠<br />\n臨崖勒馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWySPLf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWySPLf.gif&h=c325979b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再睇睇翻自己手機上面訂閱左既頻道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎緊呢7年，你係咪真係想同果D頻道一樣下場呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你比人起底既話，你既手機就冇辦法聯繫朋友<br />\n如果你分享造謠資訊，你出黎既時候係7年後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你有留言進行過造謠，都會監禁7年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wpWGMAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwpWGMAW.png&h=57ab07a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再如果教唆他人自殺，會監禁14年，21年後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你有教唆他人謀殺，最高可終身監禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你數數21年失去左幾咁多<br />\n然而你就係為左果一瞬間胡言亂語既快感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者果5毫子收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而失去黎緊21年既光陰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至於仲收睇緊造謠頻道同虛假社論既朋友<br />\n我地都好擔心你既安全<br />\n因為你分享呢D頻道，好似唔係咁安全咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJEQEUq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJEQEUq.png&h=8c00286f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n取消訂閱係最佳既選擇呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FGEtrzd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFGEtrzd.png&h=740dc44c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你可能會心諗：咁多人，冇事既<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5qYZ8W.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5qYZ8W.gif&h=8cfa22c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係每次都係架，當有人比人起底既時候<br />\n佢地既手機就會紛紛報銷，無法撥通<br />\n有D甚至係不幸既大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爭先恐後，比人報名參軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzqqEns.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzqqEns.png&h=e8a72a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係你個時候你諗下，你留言果個頻道或者群組係好穩陣唔會比人起底。<br />\n如果唔係既話，我勸你地停止造謠<br />\n小心留言，查明真相。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a537ffb16b3c704a38731cdab13caf2839bc9d","tid":1541732,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></stro